title: Amphenol Chassis Mount D-Series XLR Socket - Female
blurb:
High quality Amphenol brand 3 - pin female XLR chassis mount socket, standard for balanced microphone inputs on mixers, patch panels etc. Can be front or rear mounted in P or D series panels.
• D-series flange
• Stamped phosphor bronze contacts
• Nickel finish
• Max Wire Gauge: 14AWG
• Flammability Rating: UL94-V0
• RoHS Compliant
